# Abandoned Cart Service - Backend

## Environment Variables

```
# Database
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/abandoned-cart

# Email Service
RESEND_API_KEY=your_resend_api_key

# Server Configuration
PORT=3000
NODE_ENV=development

# Authentication
JWT_SECRET=your_very_long_secret_key_here

# Frontend URL for CORS
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:5173

# Cron Job Configuration
CART_ABANDON_TIME_MINUTES=5
CRON_CHECK_INTERVAL=* * * * *  # Every minute

# Email Configuration
EMAIL_FROM=noreply@cartreminder.com
```

## Setup Instructions

1. Create MongoDB cluster on [MongoDB Atlas](https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas)
2. Get your connection string
3. Create Resend account at [resend.com](https://resend.com)
4. Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and fill in the values
5. Run `npm install`
6. Run `npm run dev`
